scaffold-bluegin

This is a minimal starting setup for Bluegin.  Clone this repository and start
modifying it to bootstrap new projects.

Customizing the app name
========================

Rename the folders under src/ to reflect your organization.

Make the following changes:

Path                           Change
------------------------       -------------------------------------------
src/.../ScaffoldActivity       Activity name and native library name 
                               (referenced in jni/Android.mk)

AndroidManifest.xml            "package" attribute of <manifest>
                               "android:name" attribute of <activity>

jni/Android.mk                 Set LOCAL_MODULE to the native library name

res/values/strings.xml         String "app_name"

